snippet: New construction looms over the famous nightclubs that have long defined a stretch of Sunset Boulevard in West Hollywood, a transformation many find jarring.
abstract: Increasing number of high-rise hotels are going up along Sunset Strip, famous stretch of Sunset Boulevard in West Hollywood, and are beginning to overshadow area icons like Tiffany Theater and  Whisky a Go Go; transformation is jarring for some who say area will feel less authentic and real.

byline.contributor: Henry Meier contributed reporting from Los Angeles.

lead_paragraph: New construction looms over the famous nightclubs that have long defined a stretch of Sunset Boulevard in West Hollywood, a transformation many find jarring.

headline.main: As Another Club Closes, Sunset Strip’s Evolution Continues
headline.print_headline: Seedy Concedes to Construction on Sunset Strip
